"type":75,"marks":5675},"You have complete audit trails without extra paperwork",[5676,5678],{"type":149,"attrs":5677},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":1299,"content":5680},[5681],{"type":112,"attrs":5682,"content":5683},{"textAlign":139},[5684],{"text":5685,"type":75,"marks":5686},"Identities are verified while important shipment data is captured, creating a smooth gate experience that balances speed with security protocols",[5687,5689],{"type":149,"attrs":5688},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":69,"attrs":5691,"content":5692},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[5693],{"text":5694,"type":75,"marks":5695},"Benefits of Using AI-Powered YMS in Warehouses",[5696,5698],{"type":149,"attrs":5697},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5700,"content":5701},{"textAlign":139},[5702],{"text":5703,"type":75,"marks":5704},"Warehouses that use AI-powered yard management systems see significant improvements in key operational areas. Here are some of the benefits they experience:",[5705],{"type":149,"attrs":5706},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5708,"content":5709},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5710],{"text":5711,"type":75,"marks":5712},"1. Increased Throughput",[5713,5715],{"type":149,"attrs":5714},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5717,"content":5718},{"textAlign":139},[5719],{"text":5720,"type":75,"marks":5721},"With automated workflows in place, trailers can move through the facility more quickly and efficiently. ",[5722],{"type":149,"attrs":5723},{"color":2236},{"type":1340,"content":5725},[5726],{"type":1299,"content":5727},[5728],{"type":112,"attrs":5729,"content":5730},{"textAlign":139},[5731],{"text":5732,"type":75,"marks":5733},"This leads to an increase in the number of trailers processed within a given time period, resulting in a throughput improvement of 50% or more.",[5734,5736],{"type":149,"attrs":5735},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":69,"attrs":5738,"content":5739},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5740],{"text":5741,"type":75,"marks":5742},"2. Lower Detention Fees",[5743,5745],{"type":149,"attrs":5744},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5747,"content":5748},{"textAlign":139},[5749,5754,5760],{"text":5750,"type":75,"marks":5751},"AI-powered systems help reduce driver wait times by automating check-in processes and optimizing trailer positioning. ",[5752],{"type":149,"attrs":5753},{"color":2236},{"text":5755,"type":75,"marks":5756},"As a result, some operations have achieved 12% reductions in detention costs",[5757,5759],{"type":149,"attrs":5758},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":5761,"type":75,"marks":5762},". This not only saves money but also strengthens relationships with carriers by respecting drivers' time and schedules.",[5763],{"type":149,"attrs":5764},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5766,"content":5767},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5768],{"text":5769,"type":75,"marks":5770},"3. Better Resource Utilization",[5771,5773],{"type":149,"attrs":5772},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5775,"content":5776},{"textAlign":139},[5777],{"text":5778,"type":75,"marks":5779},"By using computer vision and real-time data, manual tracking methods are replaced, leading to improved resource utilization. Yard jockeys receive intelligent task assignments based on actual yard conditions rather than outdated information, resulting in more efficient use of their time and skills.",[5780],{"type":149,"attrs":5781},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5783,"content":5784},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5785],{"text":5786,"type":75,"marks":5787},"4. Greater Supply Chain Agility",[5788,5790],{"type":149,"attrs":5789},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5792,"content":5793},{"textAlign":139},[5794],{"text":5795,"type":75,"marks":5796},"The ability to respond quickly to disruptions, reroute shipments based on real-time capacity data, and make informed decisions using accurate yard visibility gives businesses a competitive edge. The system automatically adapts to changing conditions, adjusting workflows and priorities without the need for manual reconfiguration or lengthy approval processes.",[5797],{"type":149,"attrs":5798},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5800,"content":5801},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[5802],{"text":5803,"type":75,"marks":5804},"Real-World Impact: Case Examples Highlighting ROI Insights with AI YMS Implementation",[5805,5807],{"type":149,"attrs":5806},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5809,"content":5810},{"textAlign":139},[5811,5816,5822],{"text":5812,"type":75,"marks":5813},"The numbers tell a compelling story when you examine actual deployments of AI-powered yard management systems. Terminal Industries' clients consistently achieve ",[5814],{"type":149,"attrs":5815},{"color":2236},{"text":5817,"type":75,"marks":5818},"rapid ROI in under five months",[5819,5821],{"type":149,"attrs":5820},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":5823,"type":75,"marks":5824},", transforming what was once a multi-year technology investment into an immediate competitive advantage.",[5825],{"type":149,"attrs":5826},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5828,"content":5829},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5830],{"text":5831,"type":75,"marks":5832},"Detention Fee Challenge Resolved",[5833,5835],{"type":149,"attrs":5834},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5837,"content":5838},{"textAlign":139},[5839],{"text":5840,"type":75,"marks":5841},"Consider the detention fee challenge that plagues most warehouse operations. One large distribution center processing hundreds of daily trailer movements saw their driver detention fees drop by:",[5842],{"type":149,"attrs":5843},{"color":2236},{"type":1340,"content":5845},[5846,5857],{"type":1299,"content":5847},[5848],{"type":112,"attrs":5849,"content":5850},{"textAlign":139},[5851],{"text":5852,"type":75,"marks":5853},"12% within the first quarter of implementing Terminal Industries'  Yard Operating System™. ",[5854,5856],{"type":149,"attrs":5855},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":1299,"content":5858},[5859],{"type":112,"attrs":5860,"content":5861},{"textAlign":139},[5862],{"text":5863,"type":75,"marks":5864},"The AI-powered Gate Acceleration™ application reduced their gate transaction times by over 85%, eliminating the bottlenecks that previously kept drivers waiting and meters running.",[5865,5867],{"type":149,"attrs":5866},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":69,"attrs":5869,"content":5870},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5871],{"text":5872,"type":75,"marks":5873},"Cost Savings Case Studies",[5874,5876],{"type":149,"attrs":5875},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5878,"content":5879},{"textAlign":139},[5880,5886],{"text":5881,"type":75,"marks":5882},"Cost savings case studies",[5883,5885],{"type":149,"attrs":5884},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":5887,"type":75,"marks":5888}," reveal even more dramatic improvements:",[5889],{"type":149,"attrs":5890},{"color":2236},{"type":1340,"content":5892},[5893,5904,5915],{"type":1299,"content":5894},[5895],{"type":112,"attrs":5896,"content":5897},{"textAlign":139},[5898],{"text":5899,"type":75,"marks":5900},"A mid-market operator with seven facilities reduced asset search time by 90% through computer vision-enabled real-time tracking",[5901,5903],{"type":149,"attrs":5902},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":1299,"content":5905},[5906],{"type":112,"attrs":5907,"content":5908},{"textAlign":139},[5909],{"text":5910,"type":75,"marks":5911},"Multiple sites reported 50%+ throughput improvement after deploying SmartYard™ YMS with automated workflows",[5912,5914],{"type":149,"attrs":5913},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":1299,"content":5916},[5917],{"type":112,"attrs":5918,"content":5919},{"textAlign":139},[5920],{"text":5921,"type":75,"marks":5922},"Gate processing errors decreased by 75%, eliminating costly mistakes and rework",[5923,5925],{"type":149,"attrs":5924},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":69,"attrs":5927,"content":5928},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[5929],{"text":5930,"type":75,"marks":5931},"Immediate Operational Improvements",[5932,5934],{"type":149,"attrs":5933},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5936,"content":5937},{"textAlign":139},[5938],{"text":5939,"type":75,"marks":5940},"The pattern across these implementations remains consistent: warehouses experience immediate operational improvements that translate directly into measurable financial returns. You're not waiting years to justify the investment—the system pays for itself through reduced labor costs, eliminated detention fees, and increased throughput capacity.",[5941],{"type":149,"attrs":5942},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":5944,"content":5945},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[5946],{"text":5947,"type":75,"marks":5948},"Transforming the Yard into a Strategic Supply Chain Control Point with AI-Powered Solutions",[5949,5951],{"type":149,"attrs":5950},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5953,"content":5954},{"textAlign":139},[5955,5960,5966],{"text":5956,"type":75,"marks":5957},"The yard has traditionally been viewed as a passive holding area—a necessary but unremarkable space between the gate and the dock. AI-powered solutions fundamentally change this perception by transforming yards into ",[5958],{"type":149,"attrs":5959},{"color":2236},{"text":5961,"type":75,"marks":5962},"strategic logistics hubs",[5963,5965],{"type":149,"attrs":5964},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":5967,"type":75,"marks":5968}," that actively manage supply chain flow.",[5969],{"type":149,"attrs":5970},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":5972,"content":5973},{"textAlign":139},[5974,5979,5985],{"text":5975,"type":75,"marks":5976},"With Terminal's Yard Networks capability, you gain single-pane-of-glass visibility across multiple facilities. This ",[5977],{"type":149,"attrs":5978},{"color":2236},{"text":5980,"type":75,"marks":5981},"real-time connectivity",[5982,5984],{"type":149,"attrs":5983},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":5986,"type":75,"marks":5987}," means your yard becomes a command center where you can monitor asset locations, track shipment status, and coordinate movements across your entire network simultaneously. You're no longer managing individual yards in isolation—you're orchestrating a connected ecosystem.",[5988],{"type":149,"attrs":5989},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":5991,"content":5992},{"textAlign":139},[5993],{"text":5994,"type":75,"marks":5995},"The strategic value becomes clear when disruptions occur. When a carrier delays pickup at one facility, your AI-powered system immediately identifies alternative yards with capacity and available assets. When demand spikes unexpectedly at a specific location, you can proactively redirect inbound shipments to prevent congestion before it impacts operations.",[5996],{"type":149,"attrs":5997},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":5999,"content":6000},{"textAlign":139},[6001],{"text":6002,"type":75,"marks":6003},"This proactive disruption management extends beyond your four walls. By integrating shipment data and appointment information, you create predictive intelligence that anticipates bottlenecks hours or days in advance. Your yard stops reacting to problems and starts preventing them.",[6004],{"type":149,"attrs":6005},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":6007,"content":6008},{"textAlign":139},[6009,6014,6019],{"text":6010,"type":75,"marks":6011},"The shift from passive storage to active control point represents a fundamental reimagining of ",[6012],{"type":149,"attrs":6013},{"color":2236},{"text":5250,"type":75,"marks":6015},[6016,6018],{"type":149,"attrs":6017},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":6020,"type":75,"marks":6021},". You're not just moving trailers—you're orchestrating supply chain velocity.",[6022],{"type":149,"attrs":6023},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":6025,"content":6026},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[6027],{"text":6028,"type":75,"marks":6029},"Selecting the Right AI-Powered Yard Management System for Your Warehouse Needs",[6030,6032],{"type":149,"attrs":6031},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":6034,"content":6035},{"textAlign":139},[6036],{"text":6037,"type":75,"marks":6038},"When evaluating vendors, it's important to have a clear understanding of your operational requirements and long-term goals. The right AI-powered Yard Management System (YMS) should align with your specific yard complexity, transaction volumes, and integration needs.",[6039],{"type":149,"attrs":6040},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":6042,"content":6043},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[6044],{"text":6045,"type":75,"marks":6046},"Technology Foundation and Accuracy",[6047,6049],{"type":149,"attrs":6048},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":6051,"content":6052},{"textAlign":139},[6053,6058,6064],{"text":6054,"type":75,"marks":6055},"Look for a system that is built on modern, cloud-based architecture and has a track record of delivering accurate data. ",[6056],{"type":149,"attrs":6057},{"color":2236},{"text":6059,"type":75,"marks":6060},"It's important to find vendors who can provide 99% or higher accuracy in their computer vision capabilities, as anything lower can lead to data quality issues and hinder automation efforts.",[6061,6063],{"type":149,"attrs":6062},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":6065,"type":75,"marks":6066}," When speaking with potential vendors, ask them about their proprietary technology stack and how their AI models perform in different lighting conditions, weather scenarios, and with various types of equipment that are specific to your operations.",[6067],{"type":149,"attrs":6068},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":6070,"content":6071},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[6072],{"text":6073,"type":75,"marks":6074},"Deployment Speed and Scalability",[6075,6077],{"type":149,"attrs":6076},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":6079,"content":6080},{"textAlign":139},[6081],{"text":6082,"type":75,"marks":6083},"Consider how quickly a vendor can implement their solution. If a system requires extensive digging, complex changes to infrastructure, or lengthy IT projects, it can cause unnecessary delays. The best solutions are those that can be deployed in hours or days instead of months. Additionally, think about scalability—can the system expand across your entire yard network without needing separate implementations at each location?",[6084],{"type":149,"attrs":6085},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":6087,"content":6088},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[6089],{"text":6090,"type":75,"marks":6091},"Integration Capabilities",[6092,6094],{"type":149,"attrs":6093},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":6096,"content":6097},{"textAlign":139},[6098],{"text":6099,"type":75,"marks":6100},"Make sure that the YMS you choose can seamlessly integrate with your existing warehouse management system (WMS), transportation management system (TMS), and enterprise resource planning (ERP) systems. This will eliminate the need for manual data entry and provide you with real-time visibility for better decision-making throughout your supply chain operations.",[6101],{"type":149,"attrs":6102},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":6104,"content":6105},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[6106],{"text":2038,"type":75,"marks":6107},[6108,6110],{"type":149,"attrs":6109},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":6112,"content":6113},{"textAlign":139},[6114,6119,6125],{"text":6115,"type":75,"marks":6116},"The logistics industry is changing quickly, and ",[6117],{"type":149,"attrs":6118},{"color":2236},{"text":6120,"type":75,"marks":6121},"adopting logistics innovations",[6122,6124],{"type":149,"attrs":6123},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":6126,"type":75,"marks":6127}," is no longer a choice—it's necessary for survival. You've seen how Yard Management Systems powered by AI can turn disorganized yards into strategic control centers, providing a return on investment in months instead of years.",[6128],{"type":149,"attrs":6129},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":6131,"content":6132},{"textAlign":139},[6133],{"text":6134,"type":75,"marks":6135},"The future belongs to warehouses that embrace digital technology now. Picture your yard network functioning as a smooth, intelligent system where every asset is monitored, every action is improved, and every choice is based on data. This isn't just a far-off dream—it's already happening at progressive facilities across North America.",[6136],{"type":149,"attrs":6137},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":6139,"content":6140},{"textAlign":139},[6141],{"text":6142,"type":75,"marks":6143},"Your competitors are already looking into these technologies. The real question isn't whether AI YMS will become the norm in warehouse operations, but whether you'll be at the forefront or trailing behind this transformation.",[6144],{"type":149,"attrs":6145},{"color":2236},{"type":112,"attrs":6147,"content":6148},{"textAlign":139},[6149,6154,6159],{"text":6150,"type":75,"marks":6151},"Digitized yards offer more than just improved efficiency—they're the building blocks for sustainable and adaptable supply chains that can handle any obstacles that come their way. You have an opportunity right now to position your operations at the forefront of ",[6152],{"type":149,"attrs":6153},{"color":2236},{"text":5250,"type":75,"marks":6155},[6156,6158],{"type":149,"attrs":6157},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":6160,"type":75,"marks":6161},". The technology is ready. Are you?",[6162],{"type":149,"attrs":6163},{"color":2236},{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[3232],{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":6167},{},"Why Every Warehouse Needs an AI-Powered Yard Management System",{"id":6170,"alt":18,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":6171,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":6172,"is_external_url":49},110544897979801,"/storyblok/f/337048/2034x1150/c561abc6ba/r.webp",{},[],"Find out why AI-powered yard management s