750,11756],{"text":11751,"type":75,"marks":11752},"Blockchain logistics applications",[11753,11755],{"type":149,"attrs":11754},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":11757,"type":75,"marks":11758}," are emerging as powerful tools for creating tamper-proof audit trails within yard operations. You can leverage distributed ledger technology to establish immutable records of every asset movement, gate transaction, and custody transfer. This creates unprecedented accountability across your supply chain partners and simplifies compliance verification during audits. Smart contracts built on blockchain can automatically trigger payments when specific yard milestones are met, reducing disputes and accelerating cash flow.",[11759],{"type":149,"attrs":11760},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":11762,"content":11763},{"level":1432,"textAlign":139},[11764],{"text":11765,"type":75,"marks":11766},"3. IoT Sensors for Real-Time Monitoring",[11767,11769],{"type":149,"attrs":11768},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":11771,"content":11772},{"textAlign":139},[11773,11779],{"text":11774,"type":75,"marks":11775},"IoT sensor advancements",[11776,11778],{"type":149,"attrs":11777},{"color":2236},{"type":710},{"text":11780,"type":75,"marks":11781}," are enabling granular monitoring capabilities you couldn't achieve with traditional methods. Modern sensors track trailer temperature for cold chain compliance, monitor tire pressure on yard equipment, and detect unauthorized door openings in real-time. You're able to receive instant alerts when assets deviate from expected conditions, allowing immediate intervention before minor issues escalate into costly problems. The convergence of IoT data with AI-powered analytics creates a self-learning yard ecosystem that continuously refines its operational efficiency.",[11782],{"type":149,"attrs":11783},{"color":2236},{"type":69,"attrs":11785,"content":11786},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[11787],{"text":11788,"type":75,"marks":11789},"Why Yard M